# My Everything App

Personal life dashboard + AI fitness coach. Deployed on Netlify.

## Repo structure

```
index.html                              Main Everything App (dashboard, health, CRM, journal…)
fitness-coach.html                      ⚡ Fitness Coach — Claude-powered adaptive workouts
sw.js                                   Service worker (offline cache)
manifest.webmanifest                    PWA manifest
icon-192.png / icon-512.png             App icons
apple-touch-icon.png                    iOS home-screen icon
netlify.toml                            Netlify config (build, redirects, secrets-scan exceptions)
netlify/functions/garmin-sync.js        Pulls Garmin data → Supabase health_inbox
netlify/functions/scheduled-garmin-sync.ts   Daily schedule for the sync
```

## Netlify environment variables (Site settings → Environment)

| Key | Purpose |
|-----|---------|
| `GARMIN_EMAIL` | Garmin Connect login (secret) |
| `GARMIN_PASSWORD` | Garmin Connect password (secret) |
| `SUPABASE_URL` | Supabase project URL (public — also in index.html) |
| `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` | Supabase anon key (public by design, protected by RLS) |

`netlify.toml` exempts the two public Supabase values from Netlify's secrets
scanner (`SECRETS_SCAN_OMIT_KEYS`); the Garmin credentials are still scanned
and must never appear in any file.

## Fitness Coach

- Reads Garmin metrics (sleep, body battery, RHR, HRV, steps) shared by the
  Everything App on the same device (`ea-fit-bridge` in localStorage).
- Uses the Anthropic API key saved in Everything App → Settings → Voice & photo AI.
- Weather for run planning via Open-Meteo (no key needed).

## Deploy

Push to `main` → Netlify builds and deploys. Functions run from
`netlify/functions/`; the scheduled sync fires daily.
